{"tid":472810,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"[P牌］點樣做到行車置中？","createTime":"2017-11-18T14:47:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-27T03:29:13.000Z","uid":71376,"like":3,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":52,"replies":[{"pid":"6a761f93cfdff73176bf5fedca11f778cd935f68","tid":472810,"uid":71376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T14:47:45.000Z","msg":"小弟上星期終於拎到個P牌<br />\n最近拎屋企部7人車去練車<br />\n呢家行過薄扶林道、西隧同埋屯公<br />\n發覺平時開車成日偏左去右邊，太過貼右線<br />\n想問下咁多位巴絲有冇技巧分享<br />\n係可以渣車（尤其係快個陣）開得接近番兩條線既正中間"},{"pid":"4d4d5104f96319dc5fe8a03a40922ff87d4294f9","tid":472810,"uid":71376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T14:48:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc68229618405ae75110f282e62a9784fec2387d","tid":472810,"uid":140834,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T14:48:47.000Z","msg":"標準答案：望遠D"},{"pid":"eae0989b8af6b477652e3037a4cec9bb25379db3","tid":472810,"uid":71376,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T14:50:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>標準答案：望遠D</blockquote><br />\n都試緊，但有時會因為掛住望出面踩快左"},{"pid":"32dae80d25761503c8247a1b78dd367725be6278","tid":472810,"uid":71376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T14:51:49.000Z","msg":"同埋會掛住望前面同兩則而唔記得左望倒後鏡"},{"pid":"8fe22f7801588d26269951fab0ab1e8e5da9f05d","tid":472810,"uid":71376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T14:52:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同埋會掛住望前面同兩<span style=\"color: red;\">側</span>而唔記得左望倒後鏡</blockquote>"},{"pid":"b81390270ae420247ce4c5d99f1cb7f7d7a52545","tid":472810,"uid":113059,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T14:53:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>小弟上星期終於拎到個P牌<br />\n最近拎屋企部7人車去練車<br />\n呢家行過薄扶林道、西隧同埋屯公<br />\n發覺平時開車成日偏左去右邊，太過貼右線<br />\n想問下咁多位巴絲有冇技巧分享<br />\n係可以渣車（尤其係快個陣）開得接近番兩條線既正中間</blockquote><br />\n睇下架車置中時兩邊線會係擋風玻璃嘅邊個位置<br />\n我自己就習慣右線係擋風玻璃右下角，左線係擋風玻璃中間。"},{"pid":"9680fdee83466eaab4bf232fa5e8d832d6e7d3d5","tid":472810,"uid":37505,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T14:54:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>標準答案：望遠D</blockquote><br />\n望遠啲架車會定啲<br />\n應該要望多兩眼左右鏡同埋搵好啲ref point（大銀幕角位+水撥位）"},{"pid":"2843bac78384f2530cd5c5425151d3a3c77c2151","tid":472810,"uid":18241,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T14:59:42.000Z","msg":"揸得多就得"},{"pid":"5513dba8022fb36d23741b8e625f1675219cfdee","tid":472810,"uid":104021,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T15:03:12.000Z","msg":"司機位對準地下黑色油漬既右邊既中間"},{"pid":"773f427b1fbaa38430054ab87f6baf3bf5bf91c7","tid":472810,"uid":129079,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T15:09:56.000Z","msg":"條路通常中間有條黑色嘅坑(係因為啲大車行得多)，而收音機通常係車中間，當條坑上面係對住部收音機位置就得。咁你部車就會就會置中，但呢個方法唔好太依賴，望遠視線保平安！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nSorFor1999"},{"pid":"2d04bc5356c577938bfbffc233358a1549777e2c","tid":472810,"uid":11314,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T15:21:08.000Z","msg":"唔好咁留意咪錶同車速，集中望遠d"},{"pid":"505486fd4f4cd560c3361b73872238a7e3528eb8","tid":472810,"uid":78574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T15:30:32.000Z","msg":"搵架車某D位同條馬路度位<br />\n例如水撥位、鏡位之類"},{"pid":"3e17c26441ceb4d87d671f7dc7d65430f03b4f90","tid":472810,"uid":16636,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T15:32:54.000Z","msg":"對齊前車司機位"},{"pid":"28d6240b47e1432631f7f3a5094e02a12a092d82","tid":472810,"uid":7673,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T16:41:35.000Z","msg":"如果成日偏一邊<br />\n你試下感覺你左腳係正條路直中間<br />\n咁架車就會置中<br />\n教過幾個人佢地都覺得work<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee0fbb71be3568d6ea964ef25bdb675cd7b35777","tid":472810,"uid":27176,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T17:20:50.000Z","msg":"你覺得個軚盤係路中間就得"},{"pid":"346fe09ac243a4f792aa2f01be9a5e5474400d73","tid":472810,"uid":60412,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T23:31:14.000Z","msg":"標準答案：渣多d"},{"pid":"041525fae865462ebdc062d0905ba51d2da4fbbe","tid":472810,"uid":73092,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T23:33:42.000Z","msg":"召喚望遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"606fb2b4dab0744b255687e00c74bbf99655c893","tid":472810,"uid":28153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T23:44:12.000Z","msg":"感覺<br />\n<br />\n既然你都感覺到偏右 慢慢修正就可以"},{"pid":"ec10dbfd46847481727f53414779a24770a937cc","tid":472810,"uid":30922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T23:53:30.000Z","msg":"擋風玻璃右下角位掂到馬路右邊白色線"},{"pid":"8c3cd0ad61c1d0a60b9effe4b9e95a29a5e554b0","tid":472810,"uid":39139,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T06:35:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>擋風玻璃右下角位掂到馬路右邊白色線</blockquote><br />\n Agger"},{"pid":"43a191bd6144a86e03430271ec4f32ab8d3ce272","tid":472810,"uid":86418,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T06:37:40.000Z","msg":"你連軚盤都拎唔穩...<br />\n點考牌啊?"},{"pid":"9c4b3741537b0c24a12b0231a9ae6abdfa86b076","tid":472810,"uid":146621,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T06:41:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>小弟上星期終於拎到個P牌<br />\n最近拎屋企部7人車去練車<br />\n呢家行過薄扶林道、西隧同埋屯公<br />\n發覺平時開車成日偏左去右邊，太過貼右線<br />\n想問下咁多位巴絲有冇技巧分享<br />\n係可以渣車（尤其係快個陣）開得接近番兩條線既正中間</blockquote><br />\n1. 望遠少少你會覺得自己坐喺條線中間<br />\n2. 望下兩邊 side 鏡"},{"pid":"5e2600552546fc7c6806969d53fdce58924167af","tid":472810,"uid":55125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T06:42:10.000Z","msg":"真係渣多d  初頭睇a柱同條線疊埋<br />\n慢慢就望遠d已經渣得好靚仔<br />\n前面無野正常會渣快d 驚既自己買個HUD <br />\n或者開住高德 有講時速<br />\n不過我有時渣城隧 果d渣渣下發吽逗都會偏埋一邊"},{"pid":"bcb3a1d9bd2007f41d8a5dc9f452b1c9f60ca294","tid":472810,"uid":51105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T06:43:41.000Z","msg":"望前車"},{"pid":"02c10fc338532f1dd6186ff07f62b47d6983f8b8","tid":472810,"uid":82717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T07:00:35.000Z","msg":"我見有教練車貼小圓點係擋風玻璃底部 比學生睇sticker 對行車線.... <br />\n我會搵參考點, 可以搵雨刮, 軚盤, 睇鏡...."},{"pid":"0b4b9ba6082cfd4256d63ec6579ad86f5448e1bc","tid":472810,"uid":28258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T07:36:17.000Z","msg":"A柱貼平行車線，望餐d,睇兩面側鏡"},{"pid":"f882b148d3f48771730c5126d7b3b2a017036eb7","tid":472810,"uid":107436,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T07:38:07.000Z","msg":"我睇雨刮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98ee5e5d7ed95eec897a0f448b721a0364df064e","tid":472810,"uid":79410,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T07:40:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果成日偏一邊<br />\n你試下感覺你左腳係正條路直中間<br />\n咁架車就會置中<br />\n教過幾個人佢地都覺得work<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢個係好WORK. 左腳踩住馬路兩條車轆痕蹟之間個條痕.<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccb403b204ec5034497f479814ca9ded6cb75d6a","tid":472810,"uid":74171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T13:16:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我睇雨刮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n刮你個頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43c8f03f91eb6a10eeb89e6872559f12ac9a4f9b","tid":472810,"uid":88160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T13:25:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>標準答案：望遠D</blockquote><br />\n都試緊，但有時會因為掛住望出面踩快左</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n膽大心細 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲係P牌<br />\n多啲留意左右距離係咪一致"},{"pid":"caf444b377d13817e0ca9db91dbb333f7498e76b","tid":472810,"uid":152388,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T13:49:27.000Z","msg":"多望左右鏡 <br />\n靠認位都得但係你渣第二部車或者左軚車就冇用"},{"pid":"803d0daff5d544404a326f6a88b92f3e39a42209","tid":472810,"uid":85217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T13:52:53.000Z","msg":"定時望下側鏡"},{"pid":"6b999e53162be71fdae6f749e277a8b73865933a","tid":472810,"uid":12850,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T15:14:40.000Z","msg":"渣多d"},{"pid":"85d2444ddd206cef0a4f9aadea312dc1567c902f","tid":472810,"uid":40503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T15:31:44.000Z","msg":"感覺。<br />\n望遠啲，不時睄下左右鏡，修正。<br />\n要知自己架車幾大，坐喺司機位感受下架車左右兩邊有幾闊。<br />\n揸熟咗就有路感軚感，無論行車綫，定穿過泊滿死車嘅街道，都係憑感覺揸(+望鏡輔助)。"},{"pid":"16b748591714e0ae613644626615b321592acb5c","tid":472810,"uid":23063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T16:01:05.000Z","msg":"你揸車個時望多啲左右鏡<br />\n睇下架車兩邊同地下條線既距離係咪一樣 <br />\n搵架車個置中位<br />\n就睇番擋風玻璃<br />\n睇下兩邊線係玻璃邊個位走<br />\n認住個位就得"},{"pid":"69615ebf0749721a29834c955f83500914b72481","tid":472810,"uid":49,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T01:11:07.000Z","msg":"補鐘啦"},{"pid":"fb8dcd60de2d0262450614ab780cb82b90a5f78a","tid":472810,"uid":80089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T02:06:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>多望左右鏡 <br />\n靠認位都得但係你渣第二部車或者左軚車就冇用</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n睇左兩版終於有呢個答案<br />\n由學車開始已經係咁樣判斷<br />\n呢個方法仲可以順便望埋左右鏡睇埋後面情況<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3afeabbb5558d308f28a79512e7f2d31a3f6d4f5","tid":472810,"uid":92278,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T02:35:06.000Z","msg":"試下放手 等軚盤自己調整<br />\n<br />\n因為車道中間比車行得多<br />\n<br />\n已經有暗坑 所以部車就會好似行路軌咁<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">[black]btw平時邊道出沒多?[/black]</span>"},{"pid":"b228a4f23c1a418536deff8ff01a0d264d91ec0b","tid":472810,"uid":141551,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T05:04:35.000Z","msg":"個牌點考番黎"},{"pid":"a25e1b7e397f554d1306804b89058db2499bd981","tid":472810,"uid":62384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T05:09:00.000Z","msg":"多望側鏡<br />\n行返正部車<br />\n記住視右邊線位<br />\n習慣就得"},{"pid":"57b7ea5a82a9ac060241492dc12ab5850ccc1cc8","tid":472810,"uid":21028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T05:11:32.000Z","msg":"p牌係咁 揸多d"},{"pid":"6ca99aea234cc445b602495edf178b5520c35185","tid":472810,"uid":71376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T03:51:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個牌點考番黎</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n行街冇咩問題，行高速先係咁"},{"pid":"aa2e30bab8c1a688f97eaccd8001550822538059","tid":472810,"uid":21028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T03:56:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>個牌點考番黎</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n行街冇咩問題，行高速先係咁</blockquote><br />\n其實 司機個個都會修正 唔可能一轉就正晒架喎"},{"pid":"00ff8be44ce35958bf25cb83350d37883b6cb9a2","tid":472810,"uid":60522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T03:59:08.000Z","msg":"只供參考<br />\n我就望左2邊側鏡拎返個平均位 (咁架車應該係中間啦)<br />\n之後就對比下水撥同路面中間比較深色既地方而做reference point<br />\n咁揸車既時間得閒就望下reference point.."},{"pid":"7b90a0179bbc09be98605f4a3da93aa7810077b8","tid":472810,"uid":71358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T08:40:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>擋風玻璃右下角位掂到馬路右邊白色線</blockquote><br />\n Agger</blockquote><br />\nX3<br />\n<br />\n但揸得多同望遠啲係皇道，因為當你去旅行揸左駄啲ref point 就冇用了"},{"pid":"dc2dc00150601381bfd9cafb5abb64f4ee93bc34","tid":472810,"uid":54655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T08:51:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>擋風玻璃右下角位掂到馬路右邊白色線</blockquote><br />\n Agger</blockquote><br />\nX3<br />\n<br />\n但揸得多同望遠啲係皇道，因為當你去旅行揸左駄啲ref point 就冇用了</blockquote><br />\n望側鏡見到自己置中之後先睇擋風玻璃度ref point"},{"pid":"35519cb9241421092d7ad3918dbe4358f66b1d41","tid":472810,"uid":127952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T10:17:04.000Z","msg":"你個人係條線既中間 架車就岩位架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e5eec51178b41ce767cc263db641cc36dfc29b7","tid":472810,"uid":3581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T11:23:06.000Z","msg":"淘返黎架個牌？<br />\n<br />\n學車無問師傅？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27110ea21eed46c071a1b77f56768c0ee117ca02","tid":472810,"uid":39233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T13:48:33.000Z","msg":"我果時係放隻扭蛋公仔係中控台同助手位中間<br />\n擺貼啲擋風玻璃<br />\n行車果陣隻公仔對住你行緊果條線左手邊果條虛線<br />\n唔知明唔明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}